Patch 2 for version 7.8 - 1 November 2024

Changes
=======
1) Prevent radio program crashing if no Internet and no media to load as alternative
2) Correct error loading MEDIA if no Internet available

Also see README file 

To install the patch
====================
cd /usr/share/radio
wget http://www.bobrathbone.com/raspberrypi/packages/radiod-patch-7.8-2.tar.gz
tar -xvf radiod-patch-7.8-2.tar.gz

This patch only contains the smbus library 

